tables.table_schema:
CREATE TABLE provider_networks (
    id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    provider_name VARCHAR(50),
    network_type VARCHAR(50),
    contract_start_date DATE,
    contract_end_date DATE
);

CREATE TABLE contracts (
    contract_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    provider_id INT,
    start_date DATE,
    end_date DATE,
    contract_value DECIMAL(10,2)
);

CREATE TABLE contracts ( 
    contract_id INT PRIMARY KEY, 
    provider_id INT NOT NULL, 
    start_date DATE NOT NULL, 
    end_date DATE NOT NULL, 
    contract_value DECIMAL(10, 2) NOT NULL, 
    CONSTRAINT fk_provider_id FOREIGN KEY (provider_id) REFERENCES provider_networks(provider_id) 
);

CREATE TABLE negotiations ( 
    negotiation_id INT PRIMARY KEY, 
    contract_id INT NOT NULL, 
    negotiation_date DATE NOT NULL, 
    negotiation_details TEXT, 
    CONSTRAINT fk_contract_id FOREIGN KEY (contract_id) REFERENCES contracts(contract_id) 
);

CREATE TABLE provider_contract (
    contract_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    provider_id INT,
    contract_start_date DATE,
    contract_end_date DATE,
    contract_value DECIMAL(10, 2)
);

CREATE TABLE contract (
  contract_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
  provider_id INT,
  start_date DATE,
  end_date DATE,
  contract_value DECIMAL(10,2)
);
